text: Tangdong Subdistrict () is a subdistrict and the seat of Zixing City in Hunan, China. The subdistrict was formed in 1989唐洞街道 - About Tangdong Subdistrict: (唐洞街道)1988年属资兴市木根桥乡和郴县高码乡，1989年设唐洞街道. see xzqh.org (2012-02-21) and merged the former Chengshui Town () to it in 2015. It has an area of with a population of 81,100 (as of 2015), its seat is at Wenfenglu Community ().according to the result on adjustment of township-level administrative divisions of Zixing City on November 27, 2015 -《湖南省民政厅关于同意资兴市乡镇区划调整方案的批复》(湘民行发〔2015〕94号): 同意同意唐洞街道、程水镇成建制合并设立唐洞街道。新设立的唐洞街道辖17个建制村，10个社区居委会，总面积153.87平方千米，总人口8.11万人，办事处驻文锋路社区（原唐洞街道办事处驻地）. see rednet.cn (Dec.4 2015) ==References== Category:Zixing Category:Township- level divisions of Hunan
